headline: CARMAX MARKS 21st CONSECUTIVE YEAR AS ONE OF FORTUNE MAGAZINE’S   100 BEST COMPANIES TO WORK FOR®
summary: RICHMOND, Virginia, April 02, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Fortune magazine and Great Place to Work® have named CarMax (NYSE: KMX) one of the 100 Best Companies to Work For® in 2025. This marks the 21st consecutive year that CarMax has been named to this prestigious list, which annually recognizes the best companies to work for in the country.
